{"tid":57200,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"馬 蹄 露 差 啲 搞 到 無 衫 著！","createTime":"2016-12-27T21:16:54.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-29T06:12:24.000Z","uid":53178,"like":2,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"fa00cdffbbfc28a4cb378d4af83c3317146770b2","tid":57200,"uid":53178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T21:16:54.000Z","msg":"馬蹄露噚晚出發去咗重慶，因為佢入圍「2016年度亞洲時尚頒獎盛典」，所以專登搵人準備3套共10萬蚊嘅晚裝出席，點知因為航空公司嘅問題，搞到佢個人到咗重慶，不過啲行李冇上到飛機，結果要問同行嘅人借衫著。<br />\n<br />\n馬蹄露今日接受傳媒訪問，佢話：「因為航空公司話運輸上出現問題，每日都出錯，起飛後發現三件行李冇喺機上，不過0依家行李已經搵到，但係聽日傍晚先可以送到去我住嘅酒店，所以我聽日攞第一個獎著唔到我原本準備好嘅衫。」馬蹄露話事後航空公司送咗$200人民幣、一套睡衣同兩張氈作賠償。<br />\n<br />\n馬蹄露仲話：「大會聽日會頒一個入圍獎俾我，依家冇衫同日用品，好彩有同行嘅人江湖告急借衫著，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">但係好彩係搵到啲行李，萬一唔見咗就大件事，3套衫夾埋都要10萬蚊，我真係賠唔起！</span></strong>」但係始終係臨時臨急去搵，效果未必同最初嗰回事，佢話：「<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>嗰對鞋只得2吋半，已經冇咗嗰個氣勢</strong></span>，嚟緊呢幾日都會活動，等聽日行李到咗就有衫著。」<br />\n<br />\n原本霸氣造型：<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmXWqp8PqNvo7EnPhRZ2Xrs7ZhqiDJ7vTgDrsgCJEtER1Q?filename=As1Ut5d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAs1Ut5d.jpg&h=c7f6b726&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n重慶烏絲雞造型：<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmPezi2wxUjVhhEhJn4izkoMrC27vmvjFtZC1dUByzjrrN?filename=40J2kKz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F40J2kKz.jpg&h=02bfd011&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/28/051007_ad74cd4928a6b638978f8016dac24323.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F12%2F28%2F051007_ad74cd4928a6b638978f8016dac24323.jpg&h=ff372cf5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/28/051421_3ce7fb1b5a80c81ef5a884abb0fb1267.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F12%2F28%2F051421_3ce7fb1b5a80c81ef5a884abb0fb1267.jpg&h=cb5f363b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmdkBnqCz5viAbnRGUFeNrNTMvbHo9TQMLp891Ftm4J1Mt?filename=D9ri311.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FD9ri311.jpg&h=9d46226a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"67d90585fd5a0df21972ef4e7af3779a87afea68","tid":57200,"uid":37240,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T21:19:47.000Z","msg":"10萬... 咁既野？<br />\n我真係唔識時裝呢樣野"},{"pid":"50a5c8a39bde92e50ce3b061dda4c67abb06635d","tid":57200,"uid":16956,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T21:20:20.000Z","msg":"我屌點解我會入黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e08d79f0cb3f9450a583df80d68b546e8770d2f3","tid":57200,"uid":16284,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T21:20:22.000Z","msg":"佢點解會拎到獎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0a5c418c5dc953da14be6e9f44de75628a739b0e","tid":57200,"uid":53178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T21:22:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>佢點解會拎到獎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n重慶獎，阿豬阿狗齊很獎<br />\n攞完獎食雞煲<br />\n食完雞煲再食馬蹄露"},{"pid":"0ebdc6128da8f2a17087f769d3e50cf468ef8864","tid":57200,"uid":53178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T21:23:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>佢點解會拎到獎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n重慶獎，阿豬阿狗齊<span style=\"color: red;\">得</span>獎<br />\n攞完獎食雞煲<br />\n食完雞煲再食馬蹄露</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6ab1e57571fb92c1cd666cfc038573ceb8f5067f","tid":57200,"uid":7846,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T21:52:50.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"20d5a8551024f240724916d90e000f1954245c28","tid":57200,"uid":46435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27